    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You must be standing on a firm or hard earthen surface to use this technique (such as rock or stone). You slam your weapon into the ground, sending out a burst of debris that deals 1d4 earth damage per 2 levels (maximum 4d4) to the creature in the area that is closest to you.</p>\n\n\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> The first step increases the range to 40 ft. The fifth step allows you to increase the Perform Requirements by 5 to make the technique 'safe': It will not reduce a creature below 0 HP. However, doing so also incurs a -1 penalty to damage per damage die.</p>\n",
